  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the effect of medical treatment on longitudinal
      myocardial function. Patients who have been hospitalized for reasons other than heart disease
      will be examined with Transthoracic Cardiography before and after medical treatment to
      determine change in myocardial function.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
